---
description: Evaluation-first rules for GroundSealWorkflowRuntime
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- No implementation slice is complete without a stated evaluation intent.
- Prefer deterministic fixtures before live integrations.
- Track negative-path behavior, not only happy-path success.
- Treat unexplained metric regressions as blockers.
- Preserve enough evidence to understand why results changed.
